videos.description: Cole Anthony kisses a floater off the glass over a defender for his first two points at North Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Anthony scores his first basket as a Tar Heel) 2019/11/06

videos.headline: Anthony scores his first basket as a Tar Heel

videos.description: Cole Anthony gets fouled on the play and is still able to get the tough shot to fall.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Anthony draws contact for and-1 bucket) 2019/11/06

videos.headline: Anthony draws contact for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Cole Anthony knocks down the deep triple, then on the next UNC possession heaves a pass to Andrew Platek for another 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Anthony sends Chapel Hill into a frenzy with 3, assist

videos.description: North Carolina stands strong on the defensive end leading to the fast-break alley-oop to Armando Bacot.
